review_blob: Sucks. You would be better off with water rather than this... I wouldnt even call it beer... "dirty water". Still does what it promises though, having a low calorie profile and whatever, so thats why I give it a higher score.

If you are not expecting anything groundbreaking, it is very enjoyable at first. After some bottles, the taste gets really bitter and perhaps salty, factors which are not very noticeable when you start drinking.
You can almost taste the metal of the can, but anyway, you havent paid much for it. I think that it is a good beer considering the price and it is very drinkable.
